---
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const pageTitle = 'Best Noise Canceling Headphones for Work 2026';
const pageDescription = 'Honest review of budget ANC headphones. Block office noise and focus better without spending $300 on Sony or Bose.';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription} articleSchema={{headline: pageTitle, description: pageDescription, datePublished: '2026-05', authorName: 'Toolwise Team'}} />
    <style>
      main { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: #333; }
      h1 { color: #232f3e; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
      .meta { color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
      .product-box { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
      .product-box h2 { margin-top: 0; }
      .product-box ul { padding-left: 1.2rem; }
      .btn { display: inline-block; background: #ff9900; color: #000; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
      .btn:hover { background: #e68a00; }
      .disclaimer { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #888; margin-top: 3rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 1rem; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>Best Noise Canceling Headphones for Work</h1>
      <div class="meta">Updated May 2026 · Under $60</div>

      <p>Open offices, coffee shops, and home environments with kids — all destroy focus. Active noise canceling used to cost $300+. Now you can get 80% of the performance for under $60.</p>

      <div class="product-box">
        <h2>🏆 Soundcore Life Q30</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Hybrid ANC</strong> — reduces low-frequency noise by up to 95%</li>
          <li><strong>40-hour battery</strong> — 35 hours with ANC on</li>
          <li><strong>Hi-Res Audio</strong> — 40mm drivers, LDAC support</li>
          <li><strong>Comfortable fit</strong> — memory foam earcups, 260g lightweight</li>
          <li><strong>Multipoint connection</strong> — connect to laptop and phone simultaneously</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=soundcore+life+q30&tag=toolwise20-20" class="btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored">Check Current Price on Amazon</a>
      </div>

      <h3>Why it beats $300 flagships for work</h3>
      <p>Sony WH-1000XM5 blocks more noise, but the gap is smaller than the $240 price difference suggests. For office chatter, keyboard clicks, and air conditioning, the Q30 is more than enough. The 40-hour battery means you charge once a week, not daily.</p>

      <h3>Who should buy it</h3>
      <p>Remote workers in noisy households, open-office employees, and students in shared dorms. If you are not an audiophile and just need silence to focus, this is the smartest money you will spend this year.</p>

      <div class="disclaimer">
        Disclosure: As an Amazon Associate I earn from qualifying purchases. This review is based on independent research and reader feedback.
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>